Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.20,0:00:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.11,0:00:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角  追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.58,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.13,0:00:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.10,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.99,0:01:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚从“半岛”回国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.53,0:01:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿到不少关于久世的有趣情报喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.30,0:01:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,课长和少校被总理叫去了\N不在本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我们先听你的报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事啊？比这个案子更重要？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.48,0:02:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是出现了难民集体武装暴动的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.12,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,＃16  在那里的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别的11人引发自杀骚动以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对急剧增加的反难民游行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.03,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有报告说难民不断地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.83,0:02:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从位于全国的居住区集结到长崎的出岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,某些急躁的媒体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经开始鼓吹说那是难民集体武装暴动的预兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这方面情况如何了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.71,0:02:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的确接到报告显示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,检举非法脱离监视者的比率增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 要跟暴动连结在一起\N恐怕为时尚早吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正在岸边防止难民流入长崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这样说好像有点认知不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们海上保安厅这个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:03:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经阻止2艘可疑船只\N16艘小艇接近出岛海岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民流入长崎已经是不言而喻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我们另外还有很多必须要处理的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指个别主义者吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就想问公安部在做些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放任他们在本事件中煽风点火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罪过可是很重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于那些自杀的个别的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.56,0:03:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要公安部事先掌握其所在\N根本是不合理的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在大部分的个别主义者\N虽然赞赏他们的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.74,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却也都作证跟他们划清界线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.68,0:03:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这次的难民问题\N我觉得防卫省也有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对军备扩张太过痴心妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在他们面前搞实弹演习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果把睡着的人唤醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.42,0:03:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想争论先有鸡还是先有蛋的话\N在下乐意奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.19,0:04:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这段时间吵着要管辖权的\N不正是那边的警备部吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.26,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你这么说 那海自为什么\N装作一副没看到的样子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在提出管辖权问题之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你们能多协助我们这些挺身拼命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 难民问题发展至此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们认为权限应该已经移转给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.38,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回想一下前世纪的安保斗争吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然这样说对晚到的国防专业议员们很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.75,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我国的治安维持工作今后也将由警察来执行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.86,0:04:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然这些争论也很重要\N不过 现在重点在各省厅间的共识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来您连心情愉快的空间都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我能力不足也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.42,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 大家仅止于争取自身的特权\N将会看不见问题的本质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.66,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在明明是希望大家合力\N解决难民问题的时期啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.47,0:05:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您知道各国军部和谍报机关\N逐渐弱化的最大理由吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚总理说的正是原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当站在组织顶端的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始利用组织当作自身争权夺利的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,组织就开始缓慢死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.85,0:05:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 让海上保安厅扮演吃亏角色\N我总觉得过意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.16,0:05:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不一定哪时候也会碰到那种灾难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.90,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于难民的动静\N有得到什么具体的情报吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.81,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问总理知道什么是中枢(Hub)电子脑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 请你说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理 可以做有线通讯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,网络原本没有Hub也就是“中枢”这个概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.37,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有台主机定义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,网络上孤立意志的方向性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且借由邀请他们进入自己的电子脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.48,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现了构筑某种共同体的现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前那不过是以小规模宗教集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或有魅力独领风骚的艺人为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有自治团体程度的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 在难民当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.16,0:06:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎出现了有能力笼络他们\N让他们滞留下来的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.40,0:06:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们认为那就是难民流入长崎的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可以说是一个…\N所谓指导者之类的存在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从常识来看很难想象是单独一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然无法一概而论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 我不认为一个人的电子脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有能力跟300万人的意志同时感应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 您若是问那是否\N象是指导者一般的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒可以说是那样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.86,0:07:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出现那样的人物对政府而言是最大的威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请继续保持警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.87,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想借由废止难民特别处理法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制住难民特权的扩大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.61,0:07:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后从税制问题着手解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是似乎有政敌巧妙地利用了这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要太过在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.99,0:07:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有一件事要麻烦你们调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.43,0:07:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟日美安保条约有关联的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国防专业议员当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有人跟旧大日本技研有勾结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为本次安保的意义在于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让世界上唯一拥有放射能除去技术的我国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够和依靠核武吓阻力量的美帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.78,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有对等甚至更进一步的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不能达到这个目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次的安保延期签订也无妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.96,0:08:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—部分的议员和企业并不在乎这个理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.33,0:08:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这种事再重复下去\N这个国家过多久都不可能自立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个情报是哪里来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从外务省的某个管道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.01,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们就马上清查金钱的流向吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.14,0:08:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.01,0:08:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理的个人利益和政治理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.48,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该认为您是\N基于哪一边做的指示呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还用说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该更早注意到才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.54,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺总理正是课长喜欢的类型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 到现在才注意到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是败给课长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理说的国防专业议员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是指高仓官房长官吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.73,0:09:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不认为他的目的只是贿赂地授受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.10,0:09:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记得高仓不但亲美而且是新保守派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.11,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还是抛弃不了美帝盲信主义的\N“军工复合体”的最老资格者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对他来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.88,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大战结束后失去商品价值的放射能除去技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.22,0:10:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要跟美帝联手\N就可以变成对他国的新吓阻力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且提高商品的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他贿赂收贿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.76,0:10:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使军备扩张成为泡影\N还是可以保住保守派的面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.07,0:10:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这跟茅葺总理提倡的自立\N协调路线有很大的差异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他应该算是内厅的头头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上合田有在旧大日本技研
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.41,0:10:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制作“日本的奇迹”的经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.58,0:10:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引诱难民发动恐怖攻击以及日美安保条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有核武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的复仇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有参与的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你好久了 茅葺总理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我马上过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿东 有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为召集名单没有我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以不参加吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个别主义者的秘密调查做得怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些家伙比难民还没有动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们觉得好无聊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.05,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么叫作好无聊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还早得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.96,0:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候赌上欧亚霸权的\N无意义大战好不容易才刚结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我那时候虽然多次潜入半岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在可是非常近代化了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经开始了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.34,0:12:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一边等你一边热身当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多该开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.71,0:12:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才刚回国就让您过度劳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.94,0:12:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过第4次大战\N2024年时各国已经疲惫不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美帝趁大战结束的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.38,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吁联合国派兵到持续内战的半岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.38,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然这也成为派遣自卫队的直接契机…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.52,0:12:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实真相是美帝为了再度取回世界霸权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.22,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把沉睡在北半岛上的\N铀矿开采权交给统一政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.66,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才把这件事当材料利用对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.87,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 那种想法虽然昭然若揭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但日本正热烈制造战争特需物资
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能对联合国说N0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这对经历2次大战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却除了根室夺回战以外\N至今避免实战的自卫队来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:12.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根室：位于最接近北方四岛的北海道最东端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这算是首次的试炼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 老大和少校他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是在战时非公开地到海外去过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.76,0:13:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时死于炸弹恐怖攻击的首相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.29,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是少数有国际视野的政治家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.27,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因为有这些内情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.30,0:13:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府为了打压国内舆论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了严格的报导管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.31,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还决定PKF的派遣地为比较安全的新义州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到现在还记得当时的骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自卫队进入当地后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无所事事地跟居民们一起生活的报导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不觉就没人关心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半会这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然实情并非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于负责执行报导管制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幕后暗中活动的就是现在内厅的前身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内阁报导厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 PKF的真相是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.27,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我以前听说的状况更加悲惨的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世所属的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在本队中也是最后进入当地的机动部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.88,0:14:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时新义州是特别行政府也是贸易据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该在被攻击的对象之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是统一政府成立后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.93,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,败退的人民军残党所选择的最后战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在新义州东方20公里左右的农村地带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越过国境就是山岳地带吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者应该说是山顶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,标高充其量只有800米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.18,0:14:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 也算是个很适合打游击战的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达之后不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.28,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,义体化步兵部队就派出两个中队\N担任游击队讨伐队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.75,0:15:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始在极寒的山区移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.12,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是第一次正式部署到战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.69,0:15:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 对PKF型号的混合式义体来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在零下20度的雪地行军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该也不会感到有太大压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时本队收到情报显示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.61,0:15:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人民军最后的精锐部队正企图攻击新义州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此特别加强警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.11,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世的部队正准备\N从北边迂回进入展开先制攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是先行的久世这一个小队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.59,0:15:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却在流经国境的河边\N发现情报上没提到的难民营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里人民军已经徒具名号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几乎变成山贼的士兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.77,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在进行丑陋的抢劫行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.11,0:15:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世他们看到这个状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,义愤填膺地开始战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.55,0:16:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是120对30的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却在一瞬间分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.89,0:16:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世待的这个小队是义体化精锐部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是攻击难民营的这群人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.86,0:16:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说原本是军人\N却大部分还是肉身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上全部骨瘦如材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.11,0:16:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然后来收到好几次人民军的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而实际的战斗却只有这一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.99,0:16:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然极度寒冷以及不知道何时会打来的游击队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使得大家被迫处于紧张气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.29,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在市内驻扎的本队\N状态却没有那么紧绷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还记得这个影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.57,0:16:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不久之后\N农村的小队军营就出现问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.94,0:17:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PTSD吗？（posttraumatic stress disorders）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“创伤后压力症候群”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.65,0:17:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次的战斗\N而且还是单方面残杀对手的体验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢开始侵蚀年轻士兵的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的肺或脏器还没换掉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取得难民带进来的合成酒精或大麻脂(hashish)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想尽办法拼命逃避记忆中闪过的杀戮恶梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.47,0:17:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以往纪律良好的自卫队\N一旦品行慢慢开始崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本的媒体就会开始无情的批评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然难民营内杀戮的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.38,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在报导管制下完全没有泄漏给媒体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是正因为如此\N他们的态度受到强烈的批判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.93,0:17:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上下达了不让媒体报导士兵丑态的规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的自由受到限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.63,0:18:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情甚至演变到连回国都不准许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直就像隔离病房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪上加霜的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沿国境的难民营内的残杀\N被一部分媒体得知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.95,0:18:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至有人开始散布谣言中伤\N说那是不是日本自卫队干的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,农村的居民们激烈反应\N要求说明真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不要说在严格报导管制下的年轻士兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.06,0:18:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连长官们也无法为自己辩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能默默躲在帐棚里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的事情不断继续的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.31,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当地的记者对某个士兵说了这样一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙恐怕是想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.98,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挖苦这个连自己的肺都没有的士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.22,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道Assassin这个字的意思吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.96,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那在阿拉伯语的意思是“吸食大麻脂的人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.37,0:19:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十一世纪时伊斯兰的刺客会吸食大麻脂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后在梦游状态下暗杀\N夺回耶路撒冷的十字军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.64,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十字军看到之后\N就很害怕地叫他们Assassin
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.72,0:19:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也靠那玩意\N把这里看成乐园吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把军队开进别人的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算当客人当到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们这群杀人犯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干…干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们或许有当客人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以跟你交换那个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.28,0:19:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世这么说之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.88,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就拿枪交换照相机进入难民营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那他后来做了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据说什么都没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是拿着照相机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.73,0:20:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时透过取景器观看难民的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时做做折纸而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.17,0:20:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也完全搞不清楚他真正的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.21,0:20:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不久后开始出现奇妙的现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.25,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先是老人们渐渐对久世感兴趣\N到最后还请他喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.52,0:20:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来是小孩趁着叫他折纸飞机的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.22,0:20:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渐渐接近一句话都不说的久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后隔天连女人和成年男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都轮流想跟久世随便聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.43,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世却只是很高兴地看着\N然后把这个状况拍成照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.14,0:20:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持续到三个月后人民军投降\N自卫队解除任务为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.58,0:21:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媒体后来就没有人\N再提到残杀的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后自卫队归国的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.45,0:21:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世突然从难民营失去踪影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.12,0:21:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当地的难民营留有一张照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后来的行踪呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.43,0:21:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人说他越过国境向西走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过无法确定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.20,0:21:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底在哪里 如何流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.64,0:21:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查途中我跟一个自称\N从台湾难民街回来的男子谈过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.08,0:21:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说在那里见过一个\N可能是久世的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.38,0:21:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,义体的头发虽然完全变白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 他作证说那确实是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了证明是久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.52,0:21:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说久世身边总是有人\N很快乐地聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.96,0:21:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是日本人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.90,0:21:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 你会说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.35,0:22:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么 是少校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我一直在听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.05,0:22:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确实很令人感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.16,0:22:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然通过中枢电子脑的过滤阵列\N费了我不少功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于能够逆向搜寻\N难民的电子脑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.23,0:22:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是出岛的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在请NSA帮忙确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.64,0:22:33.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,National Security Agency 美国国家安全局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该很快就能用影像确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.25,0:23:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.79,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样美丽的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.67,0:23:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音\N—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字\N—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.37,0:23:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身\N—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.41,0:23:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我\N—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.68,0:23:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.99,0:23:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去让这一切成真的\N—它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.06,0:24:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.33,0:24:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音\N—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字\N—然后现出光明
